      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也很喜欢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你就是非常的有品味了",
