      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh你还在纠结这个点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "加州旅馆对指弹的技法要求非常高",
