      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "本来想安利你去运动的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "我做按摩就够了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "15:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "运动我是真遭不住",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "15:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "说到按摩，你喜欢去做哪一种？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "我有段时间也非常沉迷",
